13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明知繼續鍾意佢 只會令自己繼續痛苦落去<br />\n但係又忍唔住繼續見佢 真係好犯賤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想見咪見囉<br />\n鐘意人就要用力追<br />\n起碼你盡左力<br />\n係度叫春有咩用<br />\n佢會睇到咩<br />\n佢會知你有幾鐘意佢咩？</blockquote><br />\n利申：同緊自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f674625a13dcacff4c79cb814ee42a409bf3031","tid":444752,"uid":74764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同班同學<br />\n日日局住見</blockquote><br />\n好橙</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真係好折磨，明知冇可能，想忘記但又日日對住⋯我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779f66a8141a611a9f508587f55c91b38e00a9a7","tid":444752,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"但作為一個毒撚只會逼自己唔好搵對方<br />\n由細到大對住鐘意嘅人反而會想自己保持距離<br />\n反正都唔會有機 (我係咁諗)"},{"pid":"1286f31cc47544661a9ff9686c7d29fecd207ba6","tid":444752,"uid":151948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同自己講唔好搵佢 因為知應該冇咩可能 做個朋友唔好咩 但最後都忍唔住會搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近佢去左旅行 個心空虛左幾日 想whatsapp問下佢：玩得開唔開心啊 我好掛住你想見你啊"}]}